        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Imagine you are a marketing manager. You have heard about using AI for copy, for image generation, for campaign analysis. But every time you sit down to actually implement something, you get stuck. Which tool? What prompt? How do you chain outputs together?",
            "marks": []
