        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Generative Geniuses walks you through these exact workflows. Marketing professionals use the platform to learn how to generate ad copy variations in seconds, create visual assets with AI image tools, and analyze campaign performance data using AI assistants. The courses do not just show you the tools. They show you the thinking behind effective prompts and workflows.",
