        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "One of the things I appreciate is that the platform does not pretend AI replaces marketers. It positions AI as an accelerator. You still bring the strategy. Generative Geniuses helps you execute faster.",
