      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Team leaders and managers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " who want to upskill their entire team in generative AI. The community format and structured curriculum make it easy to onboard multiple people at once.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Career changers",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " entering the AI space who need a comprehensive foundation rather than scattered free resources. Generative Geniuses gives you a clear path from beginner to competent practitioner.",
