        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Start with the learning path that matches your role.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Do not jump into advanced modules before you have the fundamentals. The platform is structured intentionally, and the early modules build the vocabulary and mental models you need later.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Use AgentGG alongside the courses.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Reading about a prompt technique is one thing. Actually trying it in a private workspace where you can experiment freely is where real learning happens.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Participate in the community.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The forums and challenges are not optional extras. They are where the deepest learning happens. Seeing how other professionals approach the same problem teaches you more than any course module.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Revisit the platform when new models launch.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " The content updates fast. If you completed a course three months ago, check back. There is likely new material on the latest capabilities.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Build a personal prompt library.",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " As you work through the courses, save the prompts and workflows that work for you. Over time, this becomes an incredibly valuable asset specific to your work.",
