    "faq_items": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "What is Generative Geniuses and what does it offer?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Generative Geniuses is an AI education and networking platform for professionals. It offers structured courses on generative AI tools, curated resources, community challenges, and AgentGG, a privacy-first AI workspace for hands-on practice without data logging or training on your inputs.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Is Generative Geniuses suitable for beginners with no AI experience?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Yes. The platform includes learning paths designed for all skill levels, from complete beginners to advanced users. The early modules build foundational vocabulary and mental models before moving into complex workflows, so you do not need prior AI experience to get started.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How does AgentGG protect my data and privacy?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "AgentGG uses end-to-end encryption on all chats and files, never trains on your inputs, and gives you one-click session deletion. There is no logging, no tracking, and no data sharing. It is designed specifically for professionals who handle sensitive information and need AI assistance without privacy risks.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h3",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Can teams use Generative Geniuses together for upskilling?",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Absolutely. The structured curriculum and community format make it easy to onboard entire teams. Multiple people can work through the same learning path, participate in community challenges together, and use AgentGG as a shared private workspace for collaborative AI experimentation.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      }
